guiicon
Element


guiicon
&guiicon.purpose;


&guiicon.synopsis.gen;
Description



GUIIcon identifies a graphic or text icon that appears in a
graphical user interface.


Processing expectations


&format.inline; &pexp.moreinfo;




&guiicon.parents.gen;
&guiicon.children.gen;

Attributes

moreinfo



If MoreInfo is set to RefEntry,
it implies that a RefEntry exists which further describes the
GUIIcon.





See Also
&guiicon.seealso.gen;

